    "created_at": "2026-05-15T10:43:29Z",
    "updated_at": "2026-05-15T10:45:57Z",
    "body": "I've hit the same issue (not sure the same root cause). It was working in one environment but not in other. The difference eventually was the locale setting:\n\nWorking env:\n```\n$ locale charmap\nUTF-8\n```\n\nBroken env:\n```\n$ locale charmap\nANSI_X3.4-1968\n```\n\nThe setup is linux +  alacritty + zsh. After fixing the locale (ways to fix might differ based on a root cause) it worked fine.\n",
    "author_association": "NONE",
